title: What is HAPPENING in CATALONIA? How EMOTIONS shapes our BELIFES. Independence movement explained.
description:
In this video I'll try to explain how our emotions are related with our beliefs system and how they create conflicts that we might even don't want to be aware of it. 

Please, you have to understand that this is a very hard issue to introduce in some minutes, but just keep the message on it. Some times our emotions are stronger that our beliefs and we don't take them from another perspective. When you are taking part on a conflict you might not understand 100% the other part because you emotions don't allow it. 

To see it from a third perspective and empathize sometimes you have to be critic and give up on your beliefs. Am I wrong? Leave a comment please! Cheers from Catalonia, Spain.
